userInput: The Neural Priestess: In the depths of a neon-lit megachurch, an augmented woman in flowing circuitry-woven robes presides over her digital congregation. Holographic mantras spiral around her chrome-plated arms, while neural interface cables cascade from her skull like ceremonial braids. Her cybernetic eyes pulse with scrolling code as she channels the digital spirits of the net, translating divine binary into prophecies for her followers.
